message:
Hello people of Cru! I am a Nav girl who has infiltrated your page in search of two female roommates for the 2018-2019 school year. I live with a lovely lady by the name of Kristin Stomberg in Dinnaken Apartments. We are juniors who are seeking women who want to be part of a community where we can grow together in Christ!
Here are the details: two bed, one bath, four people, free laundry, $462/month, utilities are between $25-30 per month in total. Parking is available ($60/month). 
Fun facts: We have cranes on our ceiling and love to bake breads and desserts! 
If you are interested, message me or Kristin Stomberg asap on FB. 
Thanks for reading! Good luck with Finals!
